Package: TaxaWizard
Title: Conversational Workflow Designer for the TaxaID Ecosystem
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Kevin", "Lafferty", , "klafferty@usgs.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7583-4593"))
Description: Provides a conversational assistant that helps users design
    custom taxonomic identification workflows for the TaxaID ecosystem.
    Through an interactive interview, the assistant identifies required
    inputs, parameters, and pipeline steps, then generates a self-contained
    R script, methods text, or Shiny application. Supports CLI
    (readline) and Shiny chat interfaces backed by a stateless LLM engine.
